BUFFLNTH DS    CL1 .                    LENGTH OF TEXT IN DATA PORTION  28000020
*                                       OF THE BUFFER                   29000000
BUFFWORK DS    CL2 .                    RESERVED - TSINPUT USE AS WORK  31000020
